          <div data-content-element-selector="p, .js-buylink-item-container" data-allowed-classes-selector="js-buylink-item-container">
                <p>If you're lucky, you can snag a pair of <a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?fntitle=Nintendo+Switch+Joy-Con+Set+Is+Only+%2439+At+Walmart+Right+Now&amp;fnauthor=stevenpetite&amp;fndate=2025-08-29+12%3A13%3A00&amp;fnupdated=2025-08-29+12%3A13%3A42&amp;fnarticle_id=6534384&amp;fntype1=Tech&amp;fntype2=News&amp;fntype3=Deals&amp;q=https%3A%2F%2Fgoto.walmart.com%2Fc%2F1804712%2F565706%2F9383%3Fveh%3Daff%26sourceid%3Dimp_000011112222333344%26u%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.walmart.com%2Fip%2FJoy-Con-L-R-Neon-Purple-Neon-Orange%2F921709016%26subId1%3Dsubid_value&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fnintendo-switch-joy-con-set-is-only-39-at-walmart-right-now%2F1100-6534384%2F%3Fftag%3DCAD-01-10abi2f&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Nintendo Switch Joy-Con Controllers for only $39</a> at Walmart. This absolutely <em>wild </em>deal isn't available in all regions across the US. If you're eligible for the deal, you can click that magical "Add to cart" button and complete your purchase like normal.</p><p>We would not be surprised if Walmart updates the price soon. Unless the retailer is trying to clear this particular Joy-Con model from its inventory, the massive price cut may have been a mistake.</p><div data-embed-type="buylink" data-ref-id="4248" data-template="4" data-size="buylink__listicle" data-title="[Various] Nintendo Switch Joy-Con Neon Purple/Orange Deal" data-collection="" title="[Various] Nintendo Switch Joy-Con Neon Purple/Orange Deal">             <h2>                    <a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?fntitle=Nintendo+Switch+Joy-Con+Set+Is+Only+%2439+At+Walmart+Right+Now&amp;fnauthor=stevenpetite&amp;fndate=2025-08-29+12%3A13%3A00&amp;fnupdated=2025-08-29+12%3A13%3A42&amp;fnarticle_id=6534384&amp;fntype1=Tech&amp;fntype2=News&amp;fntype3=Deals&amp;q=https%3A%2F%2Fgoto.walmart.com%2Fc%2F1804712%2F565706%2F9383%3Fveh%3Daff%26sourceid%3Dimp_00